'''Michael Esser''' (born 22 November 1987) is a [[Germany|German]] [[association football|football]] [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] who plays for [[Hannover 96]].<ref name="fussballdaten.de">{{cite web | url = http://www.fussballdaten.de/spieler/essermichael/ | title = Michael Esser | language = German | publisher = [[fussballdaten.de]] | accessdate = 7 October 2013}}</ref><ref name="kicker.de">{{cite web | url = http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/2bundesliga/vereine/2014-15/49869/vereinsspieler_michael-esser.html | title = Michael Esser | language = German | publisher = [[Kicker (sports magazine)|kicker]] | accessdate = 18 June 2015}}</ref>
